data.title: Shaun Livingston Player Profile, Golden State Warriors
data.meta_description: Get the latest news, stats and more about Shaun Livingston on RealGM.com
data.text: Jun 24, 2004 - The Los Angeles Clippers selected Shaun Livingston in Round 1 with Pick 4 in the 2004 NBA Draft. Sep 1, 2004 - Shaun Livingston signed a multi-year contract with the Los Angeles Clippers. Jun 28, 2006 - The Los Angeles Clippers exercised their Team Option to extend the contract of Shaun Livingston. Jul 1, 2008 - Shaun Livingston, previously with the Los Angeles Clippers, became a free agent. Jul 9, 2008 - The Los Angeles Clippers renounced their free-agent exception rights to Shaun Livingston. Oct 3, 2008 - Shaun Livingston signed a multi-year contract with the Miami Heat. Jan 7, 2009 - The Memphis Grizzlies placed the contract of Shaun Livingston on waivers. Jan 7, 2009 - Shaun Livingston was acquired by the Memphis Grizzlies, along with cash, from the Miami Heat in exchange for a conditional 2012 2nd round pick (MEM own). Jan 9, 2009 - Shaun Livingston, previously with the Memphis Grizzlies, became a free agent. Mar 31, 2009 - Shaun Livingston signed a multi-year contract with the Oklahoma City Thunder. Dec 22, 2009 - The Oklahoma City Thunder placed the contract of Shaun Livingston on waivers. Dec 24, 2009 - Shaun Livingston, previously with the Oklahoma City Thunder, became a free agent. Feb 26, 2010 - Shaun Livingston signed a contract with the Washington Wizards. Mar 8, 2010 - Shaun Livingston, previously with the Washington Wizards, became a free agent. Mar 9, 2010 - Shaun Livingston signed a contract with the Washington Wizards. Mar 19, 2010 - Shaun Livingston, previously with the Washington Wizards, became a free agent. Mar 19, 2010 - Shaun Livingston signed a contract with the Washington Wizards. Jul 1, 2010 - Shaun Livingston, previously with the Washington Wizards, became a free agent. Jul 19, 2010 - Shaun Livingston signed a multi-year contract with the Charlotte Bobcats. Jun 23, 2011 - Shaun Livingston was acquired by the Milwaukee Bucks, along with Stephen Jackson, Beno Udrih and the draft rights to Tobias Harris, from the Charlotte Hornets in exchange for Corey Maggette, John Salmons and the draft rights to Jimmer Fredette. Jun 27, 2012 - Shaun Livingston was acquired by the Houston Rockets, along with Jon Brockman, Jon Leuer, a 2012 1st round pick (MIL own) and a TPE, from the Milwaukee Bucks in exchange for Samuel Dalembert, a 2012 1st round pick (HOU own), a conditional 2014 2nd round pick (HOU own) and cash. Oct 29, 2012 - The Houston Rockets placed the contract of Shaun Livingston on waivers. Oct 31, 2012 - Shaun Livingston, previously with the Houston Rockets, became a free agent. Nov 15, 2012 - Shaun Livingston signed a contract with the Washington Wizards. Dec 23, 2012 - The Washington Wizards placed the contract of Shaun Livingston on waivers. Dec 25, 2012 - The Cleveland Cavaliers made a successful waiver claim for the contract of Shaun Livingston. Jul 1, 2013 - Shaun Livingston, previously with the Cleveland Cavaliers, became a free agent. Jul 11, 2013 - Shaun Livingston signed a contract with the Brooklyn Nets. Jul 1, 2014 - Shaun Livingston, previously with the Brooklyn Nets, became a free agent. Jul 10, 2014 - Shaun Livingston signed a multi-year contract with the Golden State Warriors. Jul 1, 2017 - Shaun Livingston, previously with the Golden State Warriors, became a free agent. Jul 13, 2017 - Shaun Livingston signed a multi-year contract with the Golden State Warriors. Jul 10, 2019 - The Golden State Warriors placed the contract of Shaun Livingston on waivers.
